channel.title: My RSPS won't work!
channel.description: I have tried time after time after time for literally over 24 hours trying to get it to work. I have it portforwarded. The port is open. I have the no-ip set up. DUC Downloaded and running. My server won't connect to the server and the internet won't bring up the website. It either says: "Oops! Google chrome cannot connect to "D3adscape.no-ip.org"" or it will say "Page was interrupted". I have my server.java in my source set to my no-ip. My client.java set to my no-ip. and my static and in my client.java is 127.0.0.1. My gui is also set to 127.0.0.1. I have a D-link DIR 655 wireless router. What the heck do i do!?!?!?!?!?

item.title: My RSPS won't work!

item.description:

I have my server.java in my source set to my no-ip. My client.java set to my no-ip. and my static and in my client.java is 127.0.0.1. My gui is also set to 127.0.0.1. I have a D-link DIR 655 wireless router. What the heck do i do!?!?!?!?!?
